title: 08/06/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 08/06/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps last night's Hall of Fame game. Should the Cowboys be concerned about Dak's injury long term? ESPN's Sal Paolantonio discusses how realistic a Deshuan Watson trade to the Eagles would be at this point. And Vince Carter calls in from Tokyo to talk USA basketball and getting dunked on by Kevin Love.
